00:03:47.182 --> 00:03:48.640
So in this case,
this is a reaction

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:51.372
where a neutron is
heading towards,

00:03:51.372 --> 00:03:53.080
this time we're actually
going to give it

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:57.220
a label, a uranium-235 nucleus.

00:03:57.220 --> 00:03:59.770
And it very temporarily,
