00:14:42.700 --> 00:14:44.170
or slowing down.

00:14:44.170 --> 00:14:48.520
Because in addition to the
probability of any interaction,

00:14:48.520 --> 00:14:51.790
some probability sigma, if you
want to get the total reaction

00:14:51.790 --> 00:14:56.310
probability, you have to
multiply by its number density

00:14:56.310 --> 00:14:58.800
to get a macroscopic
cross section.

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:00.630
This is why I introduce
this stuff way

00:15:00.630 --> 00:15:02.310
at the beginning
of class, so you'd

00:15:02.310 --> 00:15:05.640
have time to marinate in it and
